kpi_info.use: The number of started DCH deletions for synchronised radio link reconfiguration preparations due toThroughput Based Optimisation of the PS algorithm (only SRNC). UPDATED:When the SRNC sends NBAP:RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION PREPARE message to the BTS.

kpi_info.title: ATT_MACD_SETUP_FOR_HSDPA
kpi_info.use: The number of attempted radio link setups/reconfigurations for HSDPA MAC-d flow. UPDATED: When the RNC sends NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP REQUEST or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION PREPARE with information to configure HSDPA MAC-d flow for the radio link.

kpi_info.title: SUCC_MACD_SETUP_FOR_HSDPA
kpi_info.use: The number of successful radio link setups/reconfigurations for HSDPA MAC-d flow. UPDATED: When the RNC receives NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP RESPONSE or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION READY indicating a successful radio link configuration for HSDPA.

kpi_info.title: SUM_TIME_RL_SETUP
kpi_info.use:
Sum of radio link setup time, defined as the time between the messages NBAP:RADIO LINK SETUP and NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP RESPONSE.
This counter, divided by the denominator, provides the average resource allocation time. UPDATED: When the RNC receives NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP RESPONSE.

kpi_info.title: DENOM_TIME_RL_SETUP
kpi_info.use: Denominator for M1005C243, used for average calculation. UPDATED: Updated by value 1, then the measured time is updated to counter M1005C243.

kpi_info.title: SPARE_1_IUB
kpi_info.use: Spare counter for future use. UPDATED: Never.

kpi_info.title: SPARE_2_IUB
kpi_info.use: Spare counter for future use. UPDATED: Never.

kpi_info.title: FAIL_MACD_SETUP_HSDPA_NORESP
kpi_info.use: The number of HS-DSCH Mac-d flow setup failures due to BTS not responding. UPDATED: When the RNC does not receive NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP RESPONSE, NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP FAILURE, NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION READY or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION FAILURE and a timer expires.

kpi_info.title: FAIL_MACD_SETUP_HSDPA_RNL
kpi_info.use: The number of failed HS-DSCH Mac-d flow setup failures due to radio network layer cause. UPDATED: When the BTS responds with NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP FAILURE or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION FAILURE including error cause in radio network layer category.

kpi_info.title: FAIL_MACD_SETUP_HSDPA_TR
kpi_info.use: The number of failed HS-DSCH Mac-d flow setup failures due to transport network layer cause. UPDATED: When the BTS responds with NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP FAILURE or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION FAILURE including error cause in transport layer category.

kpi_info.title: FAIL_MACD_SETUP_HSDPA_PROT
kpi_info.use: The number of failed HS-DSCH Mac-d flow setup failures due to protocol cause. UPDATED: When the BTS responds with NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP FAILURE or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION FAILURE including error cause in protocol category.

kpi_info.title: FAIL_MACD_SETUP_HSDPA_MISC
kpi_info.use: The number of failed HS-DSCH Mac-d flow setup failures due to miscellaneous cause. UPDATED: When the BTS responds with NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP FAILURE or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION FAILURE including error cause in miscellaneous category.

kpi_info.title: ATT_MACD_SETUP_FOR_DCHSDPA
kpi_info.use: The number of attempted radio link setups/reconfigurations for DC-HSDPA MAC-d flow. Includes initial DC-HSDPA allocations, reconfigurations from SC-HSDPA to DC-HSDPA, handovers and serving cell changes. Also M1005C241 is updated along with this counter. UPDATED: When the RNC sends NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP REQUEST or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION PREPARE with information to configure DC-HSDPA MAC-d flow for the radio link. The counter is updated for the primary cell.

kpi_info.title: SUCC_MACD_SETUP_FOR_DCHSDPA
kpi_info.use: The number of successful radio link setups/reconfigurations for DC-HSDPA MAC-d flow. Includes initial DC-HSDPA allocations, reconfigurations from SC-HSDPA to DC-HSDPA, handovers and serving cell changes. Also M1005C242 is updated along with this counter. UPDATED: When the RNC receives NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP RESPONSE or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION READY indicating a successful radio link configuration for DC-HSDPA. The counter is updated for the primary cell.

kpi_info.title: FAIL_MACD_SETUP_DCHSDPA
kpi_info.use: The number of DC-HSDPA MAC-d flow setup failures. Includes initial DC-HSDPA allocations, reconfigurations from SC-HSDPA to DC-HSDPA, handovers and serving cell changes. Also one of M1005C247, M1005C248, M1005C249, M1005C250 or M1005C251 is updated along with this counter. UPDATED: When the RNC receives NBAP: RADIO LINK SETUP FAILURE or NBAP: RADIO LINK RECONFIGURATION FAILURE for DC HSDPA radio link setup response. Or when the RNC does not receive DC-HSDPA radio link setup response and a response timer expires. The counter is updated for the primary cell.
